            {
               "text": "<h3>Comparing Worlds</h3>To ilustrate the difference between Babilon vision of ancient world and in the past and our actual compreension, we followed Dr. Irving Finkel's analisis. We use the map of the section <i>Maps of Ancient World: Babilonia</i>, we rotate it and we put on top of our current understanding of world, as it is shwn in this section. It is possible to observe that Babilonian conception of the world did not include nearest regions, like India",
               "source": [
